The striking new design was unveiled in Johannesburg on Thursday. Acting chief exectutive officer, Russel Paul said SAFA had decide on a separate logo for the side as they needed their own identity. Banyana Banyana qualified for this year's Women's World Cup in France but bowed out in the group stages. Sadly, the team did not qualify for the 2020 Olympic Games after they were shocked by neighbours Botswana over two legs in September.
